data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET...BUYER DISAPPEARED AFTER 60 DAYS! PRICE REDUCTION IS BELOW APPRAISED VALUE!!  This is the one you have been searching for...NO CDD...NO HOA, it is a great community where residents take pride in their homes.  This very private pool home with an AWESOME LAKE VIEW home has been renovated beautifully, high quality wood laminate throuout the house with carpet in the bedrooms, waterfall Quartz kitchen counters, shiplap feature wall, new lighting throuout, New Lg Stainless Steel Appliances, Newer Maytag Washer & Dryer, both bathrooms have been completely renovated including Granite Counters, Hurricane rated double pane glass doors in the Family room, Living Room and Master Bedroom.  New high quality ceiling fans through the home.  The garage attic has plywood installed across the trusses for lots of storage and a new Garage door opener.  Newer Water Heater, Ring camera Doorbell, simply safe security system.  AS IF ALL THE ABOVE IS NOT ENOUGH TO FALL IN LOVE WITH THIS HOME...This home has had the plumbing all redone with CPVC, the Pool an Hotub was converted to a salt water system with a verible speed pump and comes with a vacuum....Last but definitely NOT  least is this home is powered by Solar Panels with (2) Inverters that will be owned by the new owner so no huge electric bills.....I AM THINKING YOU MAY WANT TO GET A SHOWING ON THIS HOME SOON.!  HOME PASSED INSPECTION AND APPRAISAL ONLY REQUIRED TWO MINOR ISSUES DONE.  HOME APPRAISED AT AGREED PRICE...SELLERS ARE READY TO MOVE OUT OF STATE.
